# 📅 Plans

> Phased implementation roadmap for the Agents Relay module.


## Plans

---

## P1 Agents Relay — Foundation
**Status:** done
**Depends on:** G1, G2, G3, D1, D3

| Phase | Task | Owner | Duration | Dependencies | Status |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| P1.1 | Soul + Profession data model and registry | Tooling | 3 days | D1 | Done |
| P1.2 | Built-in professions (Intaker, Planner, Architect, Coder, Tester, Reviewer) | Tooling | 2 days | P1.1 | Done |
| P1.3 | Default Soul configs in `.autoforge/souls/` | Tooling | 2 days | P1.1 | Done |
| P1.4 | ModelConfig with provider abstraction and fallback chain | Tooling | 2 days | P1.1 | Done |
| P1.5 | Refactor existing Forge into reusable `AgentTurn` engine | Tooling | 3 days | P1.2 | Done |
| P1.6 | HandoffDocument schema and generation | Tooling | 3 days | D3 | Done |
| P1.7 | Context scoping: filter specs by profession | Tooling | 2 days | P1.6 | Done |
| P1.8 | Handoff compression (cheap model or rule-based) | Tooling | 2 days | P1.6 | Done |
| P1.9 | Unit tests for AgentInstance and Handoff generation | Tooling | 2 days | P1.5, P1.6 | Done |



